{
 "name": "RPlog_Dillon_and_Piper_Discuss_Kuxli",
 "title": "Dillon and Piper Discuss Kuxli",
 "summary": "Summoned to the Executive Office of the CSA headquarters on Etti IV, VicePrex Simone Drake (Piper) is confronted by ExO Dillon over the formal complaint of the young Defel cub Kuxli, who accuses her of ordering Espos to shoot him. Dillon mediates as Piper and Kuxli give conflicting accounts: Kuxli insists he was fired upon merely for trying to stay overnight with friends from Caspar and the New Republic, while Piper maintains she ordered the Espos only to keep him under guard for the good of the Authority and that he escalated by fleeing. Dillon presses Kuxli on why he defied Drake's diplomatic advice, eventually winning a grudging acknowledgment that his judgement was poor, while warning Piper that her heavy-handed actions will face an investigation. He rules that Kuxli is temporarily relieved of his duties and enrolled at the University of Kalla until deemed ready to return. Piper departs standing firmly by her actions, and Dillon holds Kuxli back to speak with him privately.",
